(24776, 10274, 0, 1, 'Never Look Back', '', '2010-05-17 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 1, 7, 'I guess our time is up, it’s the ending, let’s shake and say goodbye. A different path’s been chose\r\nThat’s what I wanted, it’s what I needed. Because you don’t need to know me, for what I’ve done, for what I’ve said. Because you don’t need to love me, I cannot take all these pains\r\nRemember the moment when there’s nowhere else to run\r\nOn the top of the mountain screaming for somewhere I belong\r\nHow many deceptions did I claim to get this far\r\nIt’s taking me down, in one way or another\r\nThe solar system break inside of me I cannot breathe\r\nI want to be alone, all alone\r\nAll the vanity that’s left in me\r\nAll the misery left won’t agree\r\nI’m trying to perceive\r\nAll the time I wasted to be free\r\nAll the memory left won’t fade away\r\nIt’s a different side of me\r\nAs I start to wonder, what’s the price I pay?\r\nTo be a different side of me\r\nAs I start to wonder, what’s the price I pay?\r\nAnd I walk away\r\nBut I’ll never look back, I’ll never look back\r\n', '', 347, '', 'CCZONE', '張以威', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-05-17 10:11:08', '2015-03-12 13:42:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(24777, 10274, 0, 1, 'Inside of Me', '', '2010-05-17 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 1, 7, 'There’s a time when I got lost inside of me, Never find the answer\r\nThere’s a morning I can’t even recall my name, What a pleasant nightmare\r\nThere’s a vision that is growing inside my head, Revolution’s coming\r\nThere’s a place where no one ever will hear from me, Out of love and nowhere\r\nWe don’t need your sorrow, everything is fine, We will live forever\r\nI’m learning to live, I’m changing my destiny, I’m so lucky to have you here\r\nI’m forcing my will, I’m making my time to remain, I’m so lucky to have you\r\nWe believe something’s there and something’s alive, Inside of me\r\n', '', 307, '', 'CCZONE', '張以威', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-05-17 10:11:57', '2015-03-12 13:42:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(24778, 10274, 0, 1, 'Your Smile', '', '2010-05-17 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 1, 7, 'Wu baby don''t leave me behind, you''re my favorite and you''re one of the kind\r\njust give me a chance and I''ll make you smile\r\nMaybe I''m not as good as you like, you''re still my favorite and I can''t leave you behind\r\nI love that smile of yours and I won''t make you cry\r\nMy world''s upside down, and it stop spinning around\r\nI rather lose it all to see your smile for a while\r\nI''d die for your kiss, die for your soul, I''d die to be the one to stand by your side\r\nand I''ll try to find my way, try to let go. I''ll try to live without you but I''ll never forget Your Smile\r\nYou''re something beautiful , you''ve got this magic that''s driving me crazy\r\njust give me a reason and no more lie\r\nMaybe I''ll never see you face again but you''re still my favorite and I can''t leave you behind\r\nI need your attention now\r\n', '', 260, '', 'CCZONE', '張以威', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-05-17 10:12:29', '2015-03-12 13:42:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
